《'''康斯坦汀：驅魔神探'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Constantine'''''}}）是一系列於2014年由[[NBC|NBC]]播出的美國電視劇。改編自[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]旗下[[Vertigo_(漫畫)|Vertigo]]標記系列的漫畫書《[[地獄神探_(漫畫)|地獄神探]]》<ref name="Huffington ref 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/11/first-trailer-constantine_n_5306576.html|title=The First Trailer For 'Constantine' Looks Devilishly Fantastic|publisher=The Huffington Post|date=2014-05-11|accessdate=2014-05-12|first=Ryan|last=Kristobak|archive-date=2017-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802200510/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/05/11/first-trailer-constantine_n_5306576.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[麥特·萊恩|麥特·萊恩]]飾演主角[[約翰·康斯坦汀|約翰·康斯坦汀]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/nbc-constantine-trailer |title='Constantine' Trailer: Hellblazer Comes to Television |publisher=Screenrant.com |date=2014-02-27 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2021-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210907022621/https://screenrant.com/nbc-constantine-trailer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/constantine-tv-show-plot-details-leaked-pilot |title=New 'Constantine' TV Show Pilot Details |publisher=Screenrant.com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209153431/https://screenrant.com/constantine-tv-show-plot-details-leaked-pilot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要製作者為[[丹尼爾·切羅內|丹尼爾·切羅內]]和[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]編劇<ref name="IGN ref 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/11/watch-the-first-trailer-for-nbcs-constantine-tv-series|title=Watch the First Trailer for NBC's Constantine TV Series|publisher=IGN|date=2014-05-11|accessdate=2014-05-12|first=Jim|last=Vejvoda|archive-date=2014-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512002249/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/11/watch-the-first-trailer-for-nbcs-constantine-tv-series|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本電視劇將會比2005年的電影《[[康斯坦汀：驅魔神探|康斯坦汀：驅魔神探]]》更加貼近原作。電視劇於2014年10月24日首播<ref name="IGN ref 1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=53186|title="CONSTANTINE" SCHEDULED FOR LATE OCTOBER DEBUT|last=Ching|first=Albert|publisher=Comic Book Resources|date=2014-06-02|accessdate=2014-06-02|archive-date=2014-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140603015441/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=53186|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年11月，NBC宣布，他們對於第一季將不會續訂13集以上的集數。但該系列仍有望續訂第二季<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/11/constantine-stop-production-13-episodes-season-1-nbc-1201294518/|title='Constantine' To Stop Production After 13 Episodes, Remains In Contention At NBC|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2014-11-24|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414191538/https://deadline.com/2014/11/constantine-stop-production-13-episodes-season-1-nbc-1201294518/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並將於2015年5月宣布是否續訂<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/DanielVCerone/status/567569469325578241|title=NBC made some early pickups but #Constantine not canceled. We'll pitch them our plans for 2nd season in May. Then they decide.|last=Cerone|first=Daniel|publisher=Twitter|date=2015-02-17|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130052/https://twitter.com/DanielVCerone/status/567569469325578241|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月8日，NBC宣布將不會續訂本系列，但華納兄弟仍再尋找其他頻道來讓本劇繼續下去<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2015/05/08/constantine-cancelled-nbc-season-2/|title=''Constantine'' Cancelled at NBC|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|work=TVLine|date=2015-05-08|accessdate=2015-05-08|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510190154/http://tvline.com/2015/05/08/constantine-cancelled-nbc-season-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原外傳對DC漫畫翻拍電視影集經營有佳的CW將接手本劇，但CW主席最終仍表示對本劇毫無興趣。2015年6月7日，製片人切羅內宣布華納兄弟已試圖讓本劇延續下去，但最終仍不可行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.twitlonger.com/show/n_1sminvn |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-06-08 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511051356/https://www.twitlonger.com/show/n_1sminvn |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[麥特·萊恩|麥特·萊恩]]在本劇完結後，有以其角色[[約翰·康斯坦汀|約翰·康斯坦汀]]身分客串《[[綠箭俠_(電視劇)|綠箭俠]]》及加入主演《[[明日傳奇|明日傳奇]]》。

== 劇情 ==
故事設定於天堂、地獄和人間共存的世界，分別存在著天使、惡魔和人類。一位掙扎於他的過去錯誤的神秘偵探和騙子約翰·康斯坦汀，有一天他被天使曼尼要求他協助應付一個即將到來的「黑暗崛起」，使得康斯坦汀試圖一邊協助曼尼、一邊保護人類免於惡魔的威脅<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-orders-constantine-mysteries-laura-702424 |title=NBC Orders 'Constantine,' 'Mysteries of Laura,' Comedy 'A to Z' to Series |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2014-05-08 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226075724/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/nbc-orders-constantine-mysteries-laura-702424 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

