* [[麥特·萊恩|麥特·萊恩]] 飾 [[約翰·康斯坦汀|約翰·康斯坦汀]]（John Constantine）
:神祕的騙子和現代驅魔神探，紐斯卡爾事件在場的一員。個性古怪、倔強，有著不太愉快的童年生活，獨自研究驅魔咒語和法術，且精通各種魔法學。凡是與自己太過接近的人都難逃一死，為了不讓自己下地獄挺身而出保衛人類對抗黑暗勢力<ref name="Deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/lucy-griffiths-harold-perrineau-join-nbc-pilot-constantine/#more-693738 |title=Lucy Griffiths & Harold Perrineau Join NBC Pilot ‘Constantine’ |publisher=Deadline |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714225511/http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/lucy-griffiths-harold-perrineau-join-nbc-pilot-constantine/#more-693738 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
:和原作不同的是，基於電視限制，因此去除掉康斯坦汀吸菸的畫面，改成捻熄菸頭和偶爾的叼菸畫面來體現身為癮君子的他<ref>[http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/135766-Constantine-Will-Not-Be-Allowed-to-Smoke-on-TV ''Constantine'' Will Not Be Allowed to Smoke on TV] {{Wayback|url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/135766-Constantine-Will-Not-Be-Allowed-to-Smoke-on-TV |date=20180401213455 }}, June 30, 2014</ref><ref>[http://collider.com/neil-marshall-constantine-the-descents-interview/ Neil Marshall Talks Constantine, The Descent, and More at Saturn Awards] {{Wayback|url=http://collider.com/neil-marshall-constantine-the-descents-interview/ |date=20140706101759 }}, June 28, 2014</ref>，這引起了粉絲的議論。此外，NBC電視劇初期設定他是異性戀而不是雙性戀<ref name="Huff1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/07/17/constantine-nbc-bisexual_n_5591483.html|title=NBC Says Title Character Of 'Constantine' Is Straight. Fans Disagree.|publisher=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|last=Roncero-Menendez|first=Sara|date=2014-07-17|accessdate=2014-08-15|archive-date=2014-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725204701/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/07/17/constantine-nbc-bisexual_n_5591483.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，轉入CW後使用雙性戀的設定<REF>
